Afrobeats songstress Tiwa Savage has made a wish list of presents she desires to receive for her forthcoming birthday. The “Somebody’s son” singer, who will be 42 in a few days, shared via her Insta stories several photos of high-end gifts she wants for her birthday. The photos she shared included: a 2022 black Hilux, designer bags, shoes, gold bracelets and iPhone. Sharing a photo of the automobile, she wrote: “Which one of my ballers can deliver 2022 black Hilux cause the Queen needs 24/7 security.”   96 per cent of Nigerian men want me badly – Bobrisky     ‘How to handle girlfriend’s incessant demand for things you…     VIDEO: Actress MO Bimpe organises surprise birthday for…   - Advertisement - Mummy Jam Jam also shared pictures of bracelets and the bags and wrote: “Ok so I know someone should be able to run one of these, this is really for your request birthday week.” Next was a photo displaying a lovely-looking pink pair of shoes. She captioned this: “Birthday wish list.” Finally, the ‘Number one African Bad Gyal’ shared a photo of the iPhone she wants and tagged three persons she hopes will come through with it. She wrote: “One of my guys can run this one o with a Goyard phone case.”